## vLLM Deployment with Tool Calling

This model supports tool calling capabilities. Use the following configuration for vLLM deployment:

{{if .HasCLIArgs}}### Required CLI Arguments

```bash
vllm serve {{ .ModelName }} \{{if index .Config.RequiredCLIArgs 0}}
  {{range .Config.RequiredCLIArgs}}{{ . }} \
  {{end}}{{end}}{{if .Config.ToolCallParser}}--tool-call-parser {{ .Config.ToolCallParser }} \
  {{end}}{{if .ProcessedPath}}--chat-template {{ .ProcessedPath }} \
  {{end}}--enable-auto-tool-choice
```
{{else}}```bash
vllm serve {{ .ModelName }}{{if .Config.ToolCallParser}} \
  --tool-call-parser {{ .Config.ToolCallParser}}{{end}}{{if .ProcessedPath}} \
  --chat-template {{ .ProcessedPath}}{{end}} \
  --enable-auto-tool-choice
```
{{end -}}
{{if .Config.ToolCallParser}}
### Tool Call Parser

This model uses the `{{ .Config.ToolCallParser }}` tool call parser.
{{end -}}
